<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 09:15:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在俄罗斯，一家新贵威士忌酿酒厂希望打破伏特加的模式</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-an-upstart-whiskey-distiller-looks-break-vodka-mould-2024-10-08/</link><description>俄罗斯可能以其伏特加而闻名，但在莫斯科以东数百英里的一个乡村，一家威士忌酿酒厂希望吸引俄罗斯人接受另一种酒。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 09:03:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-an-upstart-whiskey-distiller-looks-break-vodka-mould-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>法国干邑游说团体：必须尽一切努力避免中国关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-cognac-lobby-everything-must-be-done-avoid-chinese-duties-2024-10-08/</link><description>代表干邑生产商的法国 BNIC 机构周二表示，中国对其产品征收新关税是对欧盟计划对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税的报复，敦促当局保护白兰地行业。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 08:33:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-cognac-lobby-everything-must-be-done-avoid-chinese-duties-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，现代汽车将于下周在印度进行 IPO，筹资 30 亿美元，每股价格 1,865-1,960 卢比</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hyundai-india-ipo-open-next-week-1865-1960-rupees-sources-say-2024-10-08/</link><description>消息人士周二称，现代汽车印度公司的 IPO 将于下周开始接受认购，定价可能在每股 1,865 至 1,960 卢比（22 至 23 美元）之间，这家汽车制造商在印度最大的股票发行中估值高达 190 亿美元今年。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 08:26:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hyundai-india-ipo-open-next-week-1865-1960-rupees-sources-say-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国考虑提高进口大排量燃油汽车关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-weighing-raising-tariffs-imported-large-displacement-fuel-vehicles-2024-10-08/</link><description>中国商务部周二表示，中国正在研究提高进口大排量燃油汽车关税等措施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 07:49:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-weighing-raising-tariffs-imported-large-displacement-fuel-vehicles-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>裁判的失误让科博利在决定性破发中领先瓦林卡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/umpires-error-gives-cobolli-edge-over-wawrinka-decisive-break-2024-10-08/</link><description>在周一的上海大师赛第二轮与三届大满贯得主斯坦·瓦林卡的比赛中，弗拉维奥·科博利的得分失误帮助他取得了破发，并以 6-7(6) 7-6(4) 决定了第三盘的胜负。 6-3获胜。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 07:49:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/umpires-error-gives-cobolli-edge-over-wawrinka-decisive-break-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国经济提振消退后，矿业股下跌，伦敦股市下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/london-stocks-drop-miners-fall-after-china-boost-fades-2024-10-08/</link><description>英国主要股指周二下跌，因中国未能具体说明刺激疲软经济的财政措施，导致矿产股亏损，引发广泛抛售，而房屋建筑商 Vistry 下调年度利润预期后股价下跌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 07:41:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/london-stocks-drop-miners-fall-after-china-boost-fades-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>矿业股和奢侈品股拖累欧洲股市跌至两周低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-two-week-lows-china-stimulus-disappointment-2024-10-08/</link><description>欧洲股市周二跌至两周低点，因中国刺激措施缺乏新细节，引发采矿业和奢侈品等与世界第二大经济体相关的行业遭遇抛售。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 07:36:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-two-week-lows-china-stimulus-disappointment-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国反倾销措施令法国烈酒股下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shares-french-spirits-makers-fall-chinas-anti-dumping-measures-2024-10-08/</link><description>在中国宣布对从欧盟进口的白兰地采取临时反倾销措施后，法国烈酒制造商的股价周二早盘下跌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 07:19:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shares-french-spirits-makers-fall-chinas-anti-dumping-measures-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>新机构负责处理欧盟用户与 Facebook、TikTok、YouTube 之间的纠纷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-body-handle-disputes-between-eu-users-facebook-tiktok-youtube-2024-10-08/</link><description>欧盟的社交媒体用户将能够向爱尔兰成立的新独立机构投诉 Facebook、字节跳动旗下 TikTok 和 Alphabet 旗下 YouTube 的内容审核。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 06:33:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-body-handle-disputes-between-eu-users-facebook-tiktok-youtube-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>电动汽车关税投票后，中国针锋相对地反击欧盟白兰地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-puts-anti-dumping-measures-brandy-imports-eu-2024-10-08/</link><description>此举是北京最近表示不会征收临时关税后的一个转变。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 05:54:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-puts-anti-dumping-measures-brandy-imports-eu-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国中国ETF大量涌入，部分投资者乐观情绪正在转变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-based-china-etfs-get-bumper-influx-some-investors-optimistic-tide-is-turning-2024-10-08/</link><description>过去一周，由于中国大陆金融市场因国庆假期休市，投资者向针对中国市场的美国交易所交易基金 (ETF) 注入了 52 亿美元的新资产，一些资产管理公司希望这种乐观情绪能够持续下去。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 05:05:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-based-china-etfs-get-bumper-influx-some-investors-optimistic-tide-is-turning-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>缅甸和南海将在即将举行的峰会上检验东盟的相关性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-south-china-sea-test-asean-relevance-upcoming-summit-2024-10-08/</link><description>东南亚领导人将于本周在老挝举行会议，因为缅甸内战和南中国海日益紧张的局势有可能削弱东盟集团在该地区的核心作用。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 04:53:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-south-china-sea-test-asean-relevance-upcoming-summit-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国股市的狂热被扫了一遍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-10-08/</link><description>Rae Wee 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 04:33:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国将向黎巴嫩提供紧急医疗物资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-provide-emergency-medical-supplies-lebanon-2024-10-08/</link><description>随着以色列与真主党的战斗加剧，中国官方对外援助机构中国国际发展合作署周二表示，中国将向黎巴嫩提供紧急医疗物资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 03:03:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-provide-emergency-medical-supplies-lebanon-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯机构报告称，俄罗斯和中国舰艇在太平洋进行联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/russian-chinese-ships-conduct-joint-drills-pacific-russias-agencies-report-2024-10-08/</link><description>据俄罗斯新闻机构周二报道，作为亚太地区联合巡逻的一部分，俄罗斯和中国海军军舰在西北太平洋演习了反潜任务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 02:49:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/russian-chinese-ships-conduct-joint-drills-pacific-russias-agencies-report-2024-10-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>